{
  "stem": "4361.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we all-- it was May 6, 7-- no, 7 or 8-- because 6 it wasn't-- 7 or 8.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We went out on the highway with the Frenchmen and the four women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And a strange thing happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "It was the most beautiful morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And it reminded me of the morning that they took us from Sighet, from the ghetto, to the synagogue and from there to the train station, and how beautiful Sighet was then, and how I thought I smelled the lilac trees in my mother's garden.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And here was a similarly beautiful, beautiful May morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was still a little nippy because we came out 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were huddling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I remembered one of the Frenchmen gave me his jacket, which I kept for many years, many years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it was a lapin, a rabbit jacket, because it was chilly, and he gave me his jacket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And we were waiting for the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And then, from afar, we saw tanks rolling in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And as they passed by, several things happened simultaneously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "One, as they were watching-- they-- they were throwing cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Then, from the tank turrets, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sleepy eyes, you know, they were sort of rubbing their eyes, were looking and throwing the cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And the Frenchmen burst out into 'The Marseillaise.' And we all sang 'The Marseillaise.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I think it was the height and the end of my idealism because that moment-- and this is very clear in my mind what I thought as the Russian tanks were liberating us, the Frenchmen were singing 'The Marseillaise.' May was beautiful, pure, clean.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "The sky was blue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "The breeze was-- was like silk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And no more SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
